                <div className="mt-6 p-4 bg-brand-light/50 border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-2xl">
                    <p className="text-[10px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-center font-medium">
                        Payments are processed in USD equivalent based on current market rates. Your bank may apply additional transaction fees.
